#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If checked, overtime slip creation can be handled as part of payroll processing"
msgstr "若勾选，加班单创建可作为薪资处理的一部分进行处理"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If checked, picked qty won't automatically be fulfilled on submit of pick list."
msgstr "如勾选，拣货单提交时不自动更新拣货数量"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If checked, the full amount will be deducted from taxable income before calculating income tax without any declaration or proof submission."
msgstr "勾选后，计算所得税前将全额扣除应税收入，无需申报或证明"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If checked, the tax amount will be considered as already included in the Paid Amount in Payment Entry"
msgstr "如勾选，收付款凭证中付款金额就含税"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If checked, the tax amount will be considered as already included in the Print Rate / Print Amount"
msgstr "如果勾选，打印的单价/总额就含税"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If checked, this item is treated as drop-shipped by default in Sales Orders, Sales Invoices and Purchase Orders. The flag can be overridden on each transaction line."
msgstr "如果选中此项，则在销售订单、销售发票和采购订单中，该商品默认视为代发货商品。此标志可在每笔交易行中进行更改。"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If checked, users will not see the Confirm Access dialog."
msgstr "如果选中，用户将不会看到确认访问对话框。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If checked, we will create demo data for you to explore the system. This demo data can be erased later."
msgstr "勾选后系统会为您生成供学习探索的样板数据，样板数据使用过后可被清除"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If different than customer address"
msgstr "仅限客户地址不同"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If disable, 'In Words' field will not be visible in any transaction"
msgstr "如果不显示大写金额，任何交易页面都不会显示大写金额字段"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If disable, 'Rounded Total' field will not be visible in any transaction"
msgstr "如果禁用，“圆整后金额”字段将不在任何交易中显示"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If disabled, this role will be removed from all users."
msgstr "如果禁用了，这个角色将会从所有用户中删除。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled then system won't apply the pricing rule on the delivery note which will be create from the pick list"
msgstr "如勾选从拣货单下推的销售出库将不启用动态定价规则"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled then system won't override the picked qty / batches / serial numbers / warehouse."
msgstr "若启用，系统将不会覆盖已拣配的数量/批次/序列号/仓库。"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled,  user can login from any IP Address using Two Factor Auth, this can also be set for all users in System Settings"
msgstr "如果启用，用户从任何IP地址登录都需要双重验证，可以在系统设置中为所有用户启用双重验证"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, Tax Exemption Declaration will be considered for income tax calculation."
msgstr "启用后，所得税计算将考虑免税申报"

#. source-app: crm
msgid "If enabled, a lead will be automatically created when an incoming email is received from an unknown contact."
msgstr "如果启用此功能，当收到来自未知联系人的电子邮件时，系统将自动创建一个销售线索。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, a print of this document will be attached to each email"
msgstr "启用后，每封邮件将附带此单据的打印件"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, additional ledger entries will be made for discounts in a separate Discount Account"
msgstr "如果勾选，生成的会计凭证中包含折扣科目"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, all files attached to this document will be attached to each email"
msgstr "启用后，每封邮件将附带此单据的所有附件"

#. source-app: crm
msgid "If enabled, all outgoing emails will be sent from this account. Note: Only one account can be default outgoing."
msgstr "若启用，所有外发邮件将通过本账户发送。注：仅可设置一个默认发件账户。"

#. source-app: crm
msgid "If enabled, all replies to your company (eg: replies@yourcompany.com) will come to this account. Note: Only one account can be default incoming."
msgstr "启用此功能后，所有发送给贵公司（例如：replies@yourcompany.com）的回复都将发送到此帐户。注意：只能设置一个默认接收帐户。"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, all responses on the web form will be submitted anonymously"
msgstr "启用后Web表单提交将匿名处理"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, all users can login from any IP Address using Two Factor Auth. This can also be set only for specific user(s) in User Page"
msgstr "如果启用，所有用户都可以使用双因素身份验证从任何IP地址登录。这也可以只为用户页面中的特定用户设置"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, auto attendance will be marked on holidays if Employee Checkins exist"
msgstr "启用后，节假日存在员工签到将自动记录考勤"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, changes to the document are tracked and shown in timeline"
msgstr "如果启用，对单据的变更会被追踪记录，显示在表单下方的日志记录里"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, deducts payment days for absent attendance on holidays. By default, holidays are considered as paid"
msgstr "启用后，节假日缺勤将扣除计薪天数。默认节假日视为带薪"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid ""
"If enabled, do not update serial / batch values in the stock transactions on creation of auto Serial \n"
" / Batch Bundle. "
msgstr ""
"如果启用，则在创建自动序列 \n"
" /批次捆绑时不要更新库存交易中的序列/批次值。 "

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, document views are tracked, this can happen multiple times"
msgstr "如果启用，系统会记录单据被查看过多少次"

#. source-app: crm
msgid "If enabled, emails will be pulled from this account."
msgstr "如果启用此功能，将从此帐户提取电子邮件。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid ""
"If enabled, formula for <b>Qty to Order</b>: <br>\n"
"Required Qty (BOM) - <a href=\"https://docs.frappe.io/erpnext/user/manual/en/projected-quantity\">Projected Qty</a>. <br> This helps avoid over-ordering."
msgstr ""
"若启用，<b>订购数量</b>计算公式： <br>\n"
"需求数量（物料清单） -<a href=\"https://docs.frappe.io/erpnext/user/manual/en/projected-quantity\">预计数量</a>。 <br> 以避免过量订购。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid ""
"If enabled, formula for <b>Required Qty</b>: <br>\n"
"Required Qty (BOM) - <a href=\"https://docs.frappe.io/erpnext/user/manual/en/projected-quantity\">Projected Qty</a>. <br> This helps avoid over-ordering."
msgstr ""
"若启用，<b>需求数量</b>计算公式： <br>\n"
"需求数量（物料清单） -<a href=\"https://docs.frappe.io/erpnext/user/manual/en/projected-quantity\">预计数量</a>。 <br> 以避免过量订购。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, ledger entries will be posted for change amount in POS transactions"
msgstr "如勾选，则为POS交易中的找零自动生成日记账凭证"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, only System Managers can upload public files. Other users can't see the checkbox <i>Is Private</i> in the upload dialog."
msgstr "如果启用，只有系统管理员可以上传公共文件。其他用户在上传对话框中看不到 <i>私有？</i> 复选框。"

#. source-app: crm
msgid "If enabled, outgoing emails can be sent from this account."
msgstr "若启用，可通过本账户发送外发邮件。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, rule matching algorithm will run every hour"
msgstr "如果启用，规则匹配算法将每小时运行一次。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, sales from this item will be included in Sales Person and Sales Partner commission calculations"
msgstr "如果启用此功能，此商品的销售额将计入销售人员和销售伙伴的佣金计算。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, system will allow user to deliver the entire quantity of the finished goods produced against the Subcontracting Inward Order. If disabled, system will allow delivery of only the ordered quantity."
msgstr "若启用，系统将允许用户交付针对外包收货订单生产的全部产成品数量。若禁用，系统仅允许交付订购数量。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, system will set incoming rate as zero for stand-alone credit notes with expired batch item."
msgstr "如果启用，系统会将已过期批次项目的独立贷项通知单的入账费率设置为零。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the Secondary Items generated against a Finished Good will also be added in the Stock Entry when delivering that Finished Good."
msgstr "如果启用，则在交付成品时，针对成品生成的辅助项目也将添加到库存凭证中。"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, the amount will be excluded from accounting entries during Journal Entry creation."
msgstr "若启用，该金额将在日记账凭证创建时排除在会计分录入账之外。"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, the component will be considered as a tax component and the amount will be auto-calculated as per the configured income tax slabs"
msgstr "启用后，该组件视为税务组件并按配置的所得税税级自动计算金额"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, the component will be considered in the Income Tax Deductions report"
msgstr "启用后，该组件将计入所得税扣除报告"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, the component will not be displayed in the salary slip if the amount is zero"
msgstr "启用后，当金额为零时该组件不显示在工资条中"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the consolidated invoices will have rounded total disabled"
msgstr "如勾选合并后的发票禁用小数精度尾差"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, the document is marked as seen, the first time a user opens it"
msgstr "如果启用，用户第一次打开单据，系统就会记录单据被查看过"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the item rate won't adjust to the valuation rate during internal transfers, but accounting will still use the valuation rate. This will allow the user to specify a different rate for printing or taxation purposes."
msgstr "启用此功能后，内部调拨期间商品价格将不会根据估价率进行调整，但会计系统仍会使用估价率。这样，用户可以为打印或税务申报指定不同的价格。"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, the notification will show up in the notifications dropdown on the top right corner of the navigation bar."
msgstr "如勾选，通知将出现在导航区右上角的通知清单里"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, the password strength will be enforced based on the Minimum Password Score value. A value of 1 being very weak and 4 being very strong."
msgstr "若启用，系统将根据最小密码评分值强制执行密码强度（注：1分表示极弱，4分表示极强）。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the source and target warehouse in the Material Transfer Stock Entry must be different else an error will be thrown. If inventory dimensions are present, same source and target warehouse can be allowed but atleast any one of the inventory dimension fields must be different."
msgstr "如果启用，物料转移库存输入中的源仓库和目标仓库必须不同，否则会出错。如果存在库存维度，可以允许源仓库和目标仓库相同，但至少有一个库存维度字段必须不同。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the system will allow negative stock entries for the batch. But, this may lead to incorrect valuation rates, so it is recommended to avoid using this option. The system will permit negative stock only when it is caused by backdated entries and will validate and block negative stock in all other cases."
msgstr "如果启用，系统将允许批次库存出现负值。但是，这可能会导致估值错误，因此建议避免使用此选项。系统仅在负库存是由追溯录入导致的情况下才允许出现负库存，并在所有其他情况下验证并阻止负库存。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the system will allow selecting UOMs in sales and purchase transactions only if the conversion rate is set in the item master."
msgstr "如勾选则采购/销售订单中仅限选择物料主数据维护了转换率的计量单位"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the system will allow users to edit the raw materials and their quantities in the Work Order. The system will not reset the quantities as per the BOM, if the user has changed them."
msgstr "如果启用，系统将允许用户编辑工单中的原材料及其数量。如果用户更改了数量，系统将不会按照物料清单重置数量。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the system will generate an accounting entry for materials rejected in the Purchase Receipt."
msgstr "若启用，系统将为采购收据中拒收的物料生成会计分录入账。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the system will use the inventory account set in the Item Master or Item Group or Brand. Otherwise, it will use the inventory account set in the Warehouse."
msgstr "若启用，系统将使用物料主数据、物料组或品牌中设置的库存科目。否则，将使用仓库中设置的库存科目。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, the system will use the moving average valuation method to calculate the valuation rate for the batched items and will not consider the individual batch-wise incoming rate."
msgstr "启用后，系统将采用移动平均计价法计算批次物料计价汇率，不考虑单个批次入库汇率"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, the total no. of applications received for this opening will be displayed on the website"
msgstr "启用后，网站将显示该职位空缺的申请总数"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, the value specified or calculated in this component will not contribute to the earnings or deductions. However, it's value can be referenced by other components that can be added or deducted. "
msgstr "启用后，该组件指定或计算的值不计入收入或扣除项，但可被其他组件引用"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, then system will only validate the pricing rule and not apply automatically. User has to manually set the discount percentage / margin / free items to validate the pricing rule"
msgstr "如果勾选，仅用于验证用户手动设置的折扣、上浮、赠品是否符合本定价规则"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, this component allows to accrue amounts without adding them to earnings. The accrued balance is tracked in the Employee Benefit Ledger and can be paid out later as needed."
msgstr "若启用，此组件允许计提金额而不将其添加到收入中。计提余额在员工福利分类账中追踪，可根据需要后续支付。"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, this component will be included in arrear calculations"
msgstr "若启用，此组件将包含在欠薪计算中"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, this row's values will be displayed on financial charts"
msgstr "如果启用，该行的值将显示在财务图表中"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If enabled, total no. of working days will include holidays, and this will reduce the value of Salary Per Day"
msgstr "启用后，总工作日数将包含节假日，从而降低日薪计算值"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If enabled, user will be alerted before resetting posting date to current date in relevant transactions"
msgstr "若启用，在相关交易中将过账日期重置为当前日期前，系统将向用户发出提醒。"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, users who login from Restricted IP Address, won't be prompted for Two Factor Auth"
msgstr "如果启用，从受限制IP地址登录的用户无需双重验证"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If enabled, users will be notified every time they login. If not enabled, users will only be notified once."
msgstr "如勾选，用户每次登录时都弹框通知。否则只弹框通知一次。"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If greater than zero, this sets the maximum benefit amount assignable to any employee"
msgstr "若大于零，此值设置可分配给任何员工的最大福利金额"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If item is a variant of another item then description, image, pricing, taxes etc will be set from the template unless explicitly specified"
msgstr "如果物料为另一物料其中一种规格(多规格物料)，那么它的描述，图片，价格，税率等将从模板物料自动带过来。你也可以手动设置。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If items in stock, proceed with Material Transfer or Purchase."
msgstr "若物料库存充足，请执行物料调拨或采购操作。"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If left empty, the default workspace will be the last visited workspace"
msgstr "如果不勾选，默认工作区为最后一次访问的工作区"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If mentioned, the system will allow only the users with this Role to create or modify any stock transaction earlier than the latest stock transaction for a specific item and warehouse. If set as blank, it allows all users to create/edit back-dated transactions."
msgstr "如指定角色，则仅该角色的用户可提交过账日期早于当前物料和仓库最新记账日期（事后补单）的库存变动单据，如留空，则所有用户均可事后补单"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If more than one package of the same type (for print)"
msgstr "如果同类包裹超过一个"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If multiple Pricing Rules continue to prevail, users are asked to set Priority manually to resolve conflict."
msgstr "若多个定价规则持续生效，系统将要求用户手动设置优先级以解决冲突。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If no Item Price is found for an item in the Price List set in the transaction, prices from the Default Price List will be fetched."
msgstr "如果在交易中设置的价格列表中找不到商品的价格，则会从默认价格列表中获取价格。"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If no Print Format is selected, the default template for this report will be used."
msgstr "如果未选择打印格式，将使用此报表的默认模板。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If no taxes are set, and Taxes and Charges Template is selected, the system will automatically apply the taxes from the chosen template."
msgstr "如果尚无税费明细且选择了税费模板，系统自动从选择的税费模板添加税明细"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If non standard port (e.g. 587)"
msgstr "如果为非标准端口（如587）"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If non standard port (e.g. 587). If on Google Cloud, try port 2525."
msgstr "如果非标准端口（例如587）。如果在Google Cloud上，请尝试使用端口2525。"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If non-standard port (e.g. POP3: 995/110, IMAP: 993/143)"
msgstr "如使用非标端口 (如. POP3: 995/110, IMAP: 993/143)"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If not checked, the list will have to be added to each Department where it has to be applied."
msgstr "未勾选时，需手动将该列表添加至每个适用部门"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If not set, the currency precision will depend on number format"
msgstr "如果未设置，则货币精度将取决于数字格式"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If not, you can Cancel / Submit this entry"
msgstr "请选择以下方式中的一种之后"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If party does not exist, create it using the Customer Name field."
msgstr "如果实体不存在，请使用“客户名称”字段创建。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If party does not exist, create it using the Supplier Name field."
msgstr "如果实体不存在，请使用“供应商名称”字段创建。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If rate is zero then item will be treated as \"Free Item\""
msgstr "若单价为0则为免费赠品"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If rule matches, then:"
msgstr "如果规则匹配，则："

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If selected Pricing Rule is made for 'Rate', it will overwrite Price List. Pricing Rule rate is the final rate, so no further discount should be applied. Hence, in transactions like Sales Order, Purchase Order etc, it will be fetched in 'Rate' field, rather than 'Price List Rate' field."
msgstr "若所选定价规则针对'费率'设置，其将覆盖价格表。定价规则费率为最终费率，不应再应用其他折扣。因此，在销售订单、采购订单等交易中，该费率将填入'费率'字段而非'价格表费率'字段。"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If selected, the value specified or calculated in this component will not contribute to the earnings or deductions. However, it's value can be referenced by other components that can be added or deducted. "
msgstr "选中后，该组件指定或计算的值不计入收入或扣除项，但可被其他组件引用"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If set, only user with these roles can access this chart. If not set, DocType or Report permissions will be used."
msgstr "如勾选则仅限分派了这些角色的用户可看到本图表，否则由单据类型或报表权限控制图表是否显示"

#. source-app: hrms
msgid "If set, the job opening will be closed automatically after this date"
msgstr "设置后，该职位空缺将在该日期后自动关闭"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If set, the system does not use the user's Email or the standard outgoing Email account for sending request for quotations."
msgstr "若设置此项，系统将不使用用户的邮件地址或标准外发邮件账户发送询价请求。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If the BOM results in Scrap material, the Scrap Warehouse needs to be selected."
msgstr "若物料清单产生废料，需选择废品仓库"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If the account is frozen, entries are allowed to restricted users."
msgstr "如果科目被冻结，只允许有编辑冻结凭证角色的用户过账"

#. source-app: erpnext
#, python-brace-format
msgid "If the item is transacting as a Zero Valuation Rate item in this entry, please enable 'Allow Zero Valuation Rate' in the {0} Item table."
msgstr "如在交易中允许物料成本价为0，请在明细行中勾选允许成本价为0"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If the reorder check is set at the Group warehouse level, the available quantity becomes the sum of the projected quantities of all its child warehouses."
msgstr "如果在组仓库一级设置了重订检查，可用数量就会变成其所有子仓库预计数量的总和。"

#. source-app: erpnext
msgid "If the selected BOM has Operations mentioned in it, the system will fetch all Operations from BOM, these values can be changed."
msgstr "若所选物料清单包含工序，系统将从中获取所有工序，这些值可修改"

#. source-app: frappe
msgid "If the user has any role checked, then the user becomes a \"System User\". \"System User\" has access to the desktop"
